    <p class="cfo-quote" style="margin:6px auto 0;max-width:24ch;">It's not a better Salesforce or Workday. It's the <span class="accent">ledger</span> a workforce of people and agents never had.</p>
    <p class="cfo-body" style="max-width:44rem;margin:22px auto 0;">SaaS was built to manage people. The next decade is people <em>and</em> agents working the same plan, and nothing on your stack was designed to cost it, score it, or control it. OTP is that ledger: a cost and a result on every seat.</p>
